You cannot bump the version of x in version x.y.z.  If you would like the release version of the package to be 2.0.0 you should change the y to 99.  At release time, Bioconductor will automatically convert to 2.0.0.

Please review  http://contributions.bioconductor.org/versionnum.html


Also important distinction is that the y stays odd in devel and even in release to indicate a release vs devel version.

Cheers


