We are still on track for Bioconductor Release 3.15 for this Wednesday April 27th.  This means that tonight is the last day to commit changes to the devel branch before creating of the RELEASE_3_15 versions of your packages.  And any changes you make to your packages at this point will not be reflected in a build report before we branch.

