As clarification,  you will still be able to commit to the release 3.145branch and the devel (master) branch throughout the next release cycle. But any packages that have not been fixed for failures or bugs in devel would then have to be fixed/uploaded to both the RELEASE_3_15 branch and the devel/master branch.

